company_name: FRANZ SCHMITT OBST- UND GEMÜSEGROßHANDEL - IMPORT GMBH & CO. KG
information: The company FRANZ SCHMITT OBST- UND GEMÜSEGROßHANDEL - IMPORT GMBH & CO. KG, is a Wholesaler, founded in 1986, which operates in the Fruits and vegetables - import-export industry. It is based in München, Germany.
